#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:10
msgid "Beetroot Seeds"
msgstr "ビートルートの種"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:11
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:100 mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:9
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:102
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:29 mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/wheat.lua:10
msgid "Grows on farmland"
msgstr "耕地に生育"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:12
msgid "Grows into a beetroot plant. Chickens like beetroot seeds."
msgstr "ビートルートの作物に成長します。ニワトリはビートルートの種を好みます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:13
msgid ""
"Place the beetroot seeds on farmland (which can be created with a hoe) to "
"plant a beetroot plant. They grow in sunlight and grow faster on hydrated "
"farmland. Rightclick an animal to feed it beetroot seeds."
msgstr ""
"ビートルートの種を耕地（クワで作れる）に置いて植え、ビートルートの苗にしま"
"す。日光に当たると成長し、湿った耕地ではより早く成長します。動物を右クリック"
"すると、ビートルートの種を食べさせることができます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:24
msgid "Premature Beetroot Plant (Stage 1)"
msgstr "未成熟なビートルートの苗（1段階目）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:25
msgid ""
"Beetroot plants are plants which grow on farmland under sunlight in 4 "
"stages. On hydrated farmland, they grow a bit faster. They can be harvested "
"at any time but will only yield a profit when mature."
msgstr ""
"ビートルートの苗は、耕地で日光を浴びて育つ植物で、成長が4段階あります。湿った"
"耕地では、やや早く成長します。収穫はいつでも可能なものの、益があるのは成熟し"
"てからです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:26
msgid "Premature Beetroot Plant"
msgstr "未成熟なビートルートの苗"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:51
msgid "Premature Beetroot Plant (Stage 2)"
msgstr "未成熟なビートルートの苗（2段階目）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:77
msgid "Premature Beetroot Plant (Stage 3)"
msgstr "未成熟なビートルートの苗（3段階目）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:103
msgid "Mature Beetroot Plant"
msgstr "成熟したビートルートの苗"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:104
msgid ""
"A mature beetroot plant is a farming plant which is ready to be harvested "
"for a beetroot and some beetroot seeds. It won't grow any further."
msgstr ""
"成熟したビートルートの苗は、ビートルートとその種をいくつか収穫できる農作物で"
"す。これ以上は成長しません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:157
msgid "Beetroot"
msgstr "ビートルート"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:158
msgid ""
"Beetroots are both used as food item and a dye ingredient. Pigs like "
"beetroots, too."
msgstr ""
"ビートルートは、食材としても染料としても使われます。ブタの好物でもあります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:159
msgid ""
"Hold it in your hand and right-click to eat it. Rightclick an animal to feed "
"it."
msgstr ""
"手に持って右クリックすると食べられます。動物を右クリックすると、餌を与えるこ"
"とができます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:168
msgid "Beetroot Soup"
msgstr "ビートルートスープ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/beetroot.lua:169
msgid "Beetroot soup is a food item."
msgstr "ビートルートスープは食料アイテムです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:23
msgid "Premature Carrot Plant"
msgstr "未成熟なニンジンの苗"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:24
msgid ""
"Carrot plants are plants which grow on farmland under sunlight in 8 stages, "
"but only 4 stages can be visually told apart. On hydrated farmland, they "
"grow a bit faster. They can be harvested at any time but will only yield a "
"profit when mature."
msgstr ""
"ニンジンは、耕地で日光を浴びて育つ植物で、成長が8段階あります。ただし目視で見"
"分けられるのは4段階だけです。湿った耕地では、やや早く成長します。収穫はいつで"
"も可能なものの、益があるのは成熟してからです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:29
msgid "Premature Carrot Plant (Stage @1)"
msgstr "未成熟なニンジンの苗（@1段階目）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:58
msgid "Mature Carrot Plant"
msgstr "成熟したニンジンの苗"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:59
msgid ""
"Mature carrot plants are ready to be harvested for carrots. They won't grow "
"any further."
msgstr ""
"成熟したニンジンの苗からは、ニンジンをいくつか収穫できます。これ以上は成長し"
"ません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:99
msgid "Carrot"
msgstr "ニンジン"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:101
msgid "Carrots can be eaten and planted. Pigs and rabbits like carrots."
msgstr ""
"ニンジンは食べてもいいし、植えてもいいでしょう。ブタやウサギはニンジンが好き"
"です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:102
msgid ""
"Hold it in your hand and rightclick to eat it. Place it on top of farmland "
"to plant the carrot. It grows in sunlight and grows faster on hydrated "
"farmland. Rightclick an animal to feed it."
msgstr ""
"手に持って右クリックすると食べます。耕地に置くとニンジンを植えます。日光で育"
"ち、湿った耕地では早く育ちます。動物を右クリックすると餌付けできます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:117
msgid "Golden Carrot"
msgstr "金のニンジン"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/carrots.lua:118
msgid ""
"A golden carrot is a precious food item which can be eaten. It is really, "
"really filling!"
msgstr ""
"金のニンジンは貴重な食料アイテムです。これは本当に、マジで食べ応えがありま"
"す！"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:29
msgid "Turns block into farmland"
msgstr "ブロックを耕地にする"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:30
msgid ""
"Hoes are essential tools for growing crops. They are used to create farmland "
"in order to plant seeds on it. Hoes can also be used as very weak weapons in "
"a pinch."
msgstr ""
"クワは農作物を育てるのに欠かせない道具です。種を植えるための耕地を作るのに使"
"います。また、いざというときには、非常に弱い武器としても使えます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:31
msgid ""
"Use the hoe on a cultivatable block (by rightclicking it) to turn it into "
"farmland. Dirt, grass blocks and grass paths are cultivatable blocks. Using "
"a hoe on coarse dirt turns it into dirt."
msgstr ""
"耕せるブロックに（右クリックで）クワを使うと耕地になります。土、草原、オフ"
"ロードは耕せるブロックです。粗い土にクワを使うと、土になります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:64
msgid "Wood Hoe"
msgstr "木製のクワ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:74
msgid "Stone Hoe"
msgstr "石のクワ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:82
msgid "Copper Hoe"
msgstr ""

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:91
msgid "Iron Hoe"
msgstr "鉄のクワ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:100
msgid "Golden Hoe"
msgstr "金のクワ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:109
msgid "Diamond Hoe"
msgstr "ダイヤモンドのクワ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/hoes.lua:119
msgid "Netherite Hoe"
msgstr "ネザライトのクワ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:8
msgid "Melon Seeds"
msgstr "スイカの種"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:10
msgid ""
"Grows into a melon stem which in turn grows melons. Chickens like melon "
"seeds."
msgstr ""
"成長するとスイカの茎になり、そこからスイカがなります。ニワトリはこの種が好き"
"です。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:11
msgid ""
"Place the melon seeds on farmland (which can be created with a hoe) to plant "
"a melon stem. Melon stems grow in sunlight and grow faster on hydrated "
"farmland. When mature, the stem will attempt to grow a melon at the side. "
"Rightclick an animal to feed it melon seeds."
msgstr ""
"スイカの種を耕地（クワで作れる）に置いて植え、スイカの茎にします。茎は日光で"
"育ち、湿った耕地では早く育ちます。成熟すると、茎の隣にスイカを実らせようとし"
"ます。動物を右クリックすると、スイカの種を食べさせることができます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:23
msgid "Melon"
msgstr "スイカ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:24
msgid ""
"A melon is a block which can be grown from melon stems, which in turn are "
"grown from melon seeds. It can be harvested for melon slices."
msgstr ""
"スイカは、スイカの種から育つ茎を経て実るブロックです。収穫してスイカの薄切り"
"にできます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:86
msgid "Premature Melon Stem"
msgstr "未成熟なスイカの茎"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:87
msgid ""
"Melon stems grow on farmland in 8 stages. On hydrated farmland, the growth "
"is a bit quicker. Mature melon stems are able to grow melons."
msgstr ""
"スイカの茎は耕地で育つ植物で、成長が8段階あります。湿った耕地では、やや早く成"
"長します。成熟したスイカの茎は、スイカを実らせることができます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:92
msgid "Premature Melon Stem (Stage @1)"
msgstr "未成熟なスイカの茎（@1段階目）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:120
msgid "Mature Melon Stem"
msgstr "成熟したスイカの茎"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:122
msgid ""
"A mature melon stem attempts to grow a melon at one of its four adjacent "
"blocks. A melon can only grow on top of farmland, dirt, or a grass block. "
"When a melon is next to a melon stem, the melon stem immediately bends and "
"connects to the melon. While connected, a melon stem can't grow another "
"melon. As soon all melons around the stem have been removed, it loses the "
"connection and is ready to grow another melon."
msgstr ""
"成熟したスイカの茎は、隣接する4つのブロックのいずれかでスイカを実らせようとし"
"ます。実るのは、耕地、土、草原の上だけです。スイカの茎の隣にスイカがあると、"
"茎はすぐに曲がってスイカにつながります。つながっている間は、他のスイカを実ら"
"せられません。茎の周りのスイカをすべて取り除くと、接続が切れて次のスイカが実"
"るようになります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:138
msgid "Melon Slice"
msgstr "スイカの薄切り"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/melon.lua:139 mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/wheat.lua:140
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/wheat.lua:148
msgid "This is a food item which can be eaten."
msgstr "これは食用アイテムです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:25
msgid "Premature Potato Plant"
msgstr "未成熟なジャガイモの苗"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:26
msgid ""
"Potato plants are plants which grow on farmland under sunlight in 8 stages, "
"but only 4 stages can be visually told apart. On hydrated farmland, they "
"grow a bit faster. They can be harvested at any time but will only yield a "
"profit when mature."
msgstr ""
"ジャガイモは、耕地で日光を浴びて育つ植物で、成長が8段階あります。ただし目視で"
"見分けられるのは4段階だけです。湿った耕地では、やや早く成長します。収穫はいつ"
"でも可能なものの、益があるのは成熟してからです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:33
msgid "Premature Potato Plant (Stage @1)"
msgstr "未成熟なジャガイモの苗（@1段階目）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:61
msgid "Mature Potato Plant"
msgstr "成熟したジャガイモの苗"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:62
msgid ""
"Mature potato plants are ready to be harvested for potatoes. They won't grow "
"any further."
msgstr ""
"成熟したジャガイモの苗からは、ジャガイモをいくつか収穫できます。これ以上は成"
"長しません。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:101
msgid "Potato"
msgstr "ジャガイモ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:103
msgid ""
"Potatoes are food items which can be eaten, cooked in the furnace and "
"planted. Pigs like potatoes."
msgstr ""
"ジャガイモはそのまま食べるも良し、かまどで焼くも良し。植えるのもいいでしょ"
"う。ブタはジャガイモが好きです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:104
msgid ""
"Hold it in your hand and rightclick to eat it. Place it on top of farmland "
"to plant it. It grows in sunlight and grows faster on hydrated farmland. "
"Rightclick an animal to feed it."
msgstr ""
"手に持って右クリックすると食べます。耕地に置くとジャガイモを植えます。日光で"
"育ち、湿った耕地では早く育ちます。動物を右クリックすると餌付けできます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:120
msgid "Baked Potato"
msgstr "ベイクドポテト"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:121
msgid ""
"Baked potatoes are food items which are more filling than the unbaked ones."
msgstr ""
"ベイクドポテトは、焼いていないものよりも食べ応えがある食料アイテムです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:128
msgid "Poisonous Potato"
msgstr "芽吹いたジャガイモ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:129
msgid "60% chance of poisoning"
msgstr "60%の確率で食あたり"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/potatoes.lua:130
msgid ""
"This potato doesn't look too healthy. You can eat it to restore hunger "
"points, but there's a 60% chance it will poison you briefly."
msgstr ""
"このジャガイモは、あまり体によくなさそうです。食べると満腹度が多めに回復する"
"ものの、短時間の食中毒を引き起こす確率が60%あります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:28
msgid "Pumpkin Seeds"
msgstr "カボチャの種"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:30
msgid ""
"Grows into a pumpkin stem which in turn grows pumpkins. Chickens like "
"pumpkin seeds."
msgstr ""
"成長するとカボチャの茎になり、そこからカボチャがなります。ニワトリはこの種が"
"好きです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:31
msgid ""
"Place the pumpkin seeds on farmland (which can be created with a hoe) to "
"plant a pumpkin stem. Pumpkin stems grow in sunlight and grow faster on "
"hydrated farmland. When mature, the stem attempts to grow a pumpkin next to "
"it. Rightclick an animal to feed it pumpkin seeds."
msgstr ""
"カボチャの種を耕地（クワで作れる）に置いて植え、カボチャの茎にします。茎は日"
"光で育ち、湿った耕地では早く育ちます。成熟すると、茎の隣にカボチャを実らせよ"
"うとします。動物を右クリックすると、カボチャの種を食べさせることができます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:71
msgid "Premature Pumpkin Stem"
msgstr "未成熟なカボチャの茎"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:72
msgid ""
"Pumpkin stems grow on farmland in 8 stages. On hydrated farmland, the growth "
"is a bit quicker. Mature pumpkin stems are able to grow pumpkins."
msgstr ""
"カボチャの茎は耕地で育つ植物で、成長が8段階あります。湿った耕地では、やや早く"
"成長します。成熟したカボチャの茎は、カボチャを実らせることができます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:77
msgid "Premature Pumpkin Stem (Stage @1)"
msgstr "未成熟なカボチャの茎（@1段階目）"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:105
msgid "Mature Pumpkin Stem"
msgstr "成熟したカボチャの茎"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:106
msgid ""
"A mature pumpkin stem attempts to grow a pumpkin at one of its four adjacent "
"blocks. A pumpkin can only grow on top of farmland, dirt or a grass block. "
"When a pumpkin is next to a pumpkin stem, the pumpkin stem immediately bends "
"and connects to the pumpkin. A connected pumpkin stem can't grow another "
"pumpkin. As soon all pumpkins around the stem have been removed, it loses "
"the connection and is ready to grow another pumpkin."
msgstr ""
"成熟したカボチャの茎は、隣接する4つのブロックのいずれかでカボチャを実らせよう"
"とします。実るのは、耕地、土、草原の上だけです。カボチャの茎の隣にカボチャが"
"あると、茎はすぐに曲がってカボチャにつながります。つながっている間は、他のカ"
"ボチャを実らせられません。茎の周りのカボチャをすべて取り除くと、接続が切れて"
"次のカボチャが実るようになります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:115
msgid "Faceless Pumpkin"
msgstr "顔のないカボチャ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:116
msgid ""
"A faceless pumpkin is a decorative block. It can be carved with shears to "
"obtain pumpkin seeds."
msgstr ""
"顔のないカボチャは装飾ブロックです。これをハサミで彫ると、カボチャの種が得ら"
"れます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:117
msgid ""
"To carve a face into the pumpkin, use the shears on the side you want to "
"carve."
msgstr "カボチャに顔を彫るには、彫りたい方の面にハサミを使います。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:132
msgid "Pumpkin"
msgstr "カボチャ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:133
msgid ""
"A pumpkin can be worn as a helmet. Pumpkins grow from pumpkin stems, which "
"in turn grow from pumpkin seeds."
msgstr ""
"カボチャは、カボチャの種から育つ茎を経て実ります。ハサミで彫るとヘルメットと"
"して被る事もできます。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:228
msgid "Jack o'Lantern"
msgstr "ジャック・オー・ランタン"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:229
msgid ""
"A jack o'lantern is a traditional Halloween decoration made from a pumpkin. "
"It glows brightly."
msgstr ""
"ジャック・オー・ランタンとは、カボチャから作られるハロウィンの伝統的な飾りで"
"す。明るく光ります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:260
msgid "Pumpkin Pie"
msgstr "パンプキンパイ"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/pumpkin.lua:261
msgid "A pumpkin pie is a tasty food item which can be eaten."
msgstr "パンプキンパイは、美味しくいただける食料アイテムです。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/soil.lua:5
msgid "Farmland"
msgstr "耕地"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/soil.lua:6
msgid "Surface for crops"
msgstr "農作物用地面"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/soil.lua:6
msgid "Can become wet"
msgstr "潤いが得られる"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/soil.lua:7
msgid ""
"Farmland is used for farming, a necessary surface to plant crops. It is "
"created when a hoe is used on dirt or a similar block. Plants are able to "
"grow on farmland, but slowly. Farmland will become hydrated farmland (on "
"which plants grow faster) when it rains or a water source is nearby. This "
"block will turn back to dirt when a solid block appears above it or a piston "
"arm extends above it."
msgstr ""
"耕地とは農業に使うもので、作物の栽培に必要な地面のことです。土やそれに近いブ"
"ロックの上でクワを使うとできます。たんなる耕地の上でも植物は育ちますが、その"
"スピードはゆるやかです。雨が降ったり、水源が近くにあったりすると、耕地は"
"「湿った耕地」となります（植物の成長が早くなります）。上に固体ブロックが現れ"
"たり、上にピストンアームが伸びたりすると、このブロックは土に戻ります。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/soil.lua:30
msgid "Hydrated Farmland"
msgstr "湿った耕地"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_farming/soil.lua:31
msgid ""
"Hydrated farmland is used in farming, this is where you can plant and grow "
"some plants. It is created when farmland is under rain or near water. "
"Without water, this block will dry out eventually. This block will turn back "
"to dirt when a solid block appears above it or a piston arm extends above it."
msgstr ""
"湿った耕地は農業に使われるもので、ここに何らかの作物を植えて育てられます。耕"
"地が雨に降られたり水辺にある場合、これが出来上がります。水がなければ、やがて"
"乾いてしまいます。上に固体ブロックが現れたり、上にピストンアームが伸びたりす"
"ると、このブロックは土に戻ります。"

